'''火山泥流'''（Lahar，源自[[印度尼西亞|印度尼西亞]][[爪哇語|爪哇語]]）是從[[火山|火山]]向下流的[[泥石流|泥石流]]或[[山崩|山崩]]，主要物質是[[火山碎屑岩|火山碎屑岩]]和[[水|水]]，泥石可以高達每小時100公里的速度前進超過300公里，對途經的地方造成災難性的破壞<ref name="hoblitt">{{cite journal|url=http://vulcan.wr.usgs.gov/Hazards/NRC_Report/nrc_hazards.html|title=Volcanic Hazards with Regard to Siting Nuclear-Power Plants in the Pacific Northwest|last=Hoblitt|first=R.P.|coauthors=Miller, C.D., and Scott, W.E.|journal=U.S. Geological Survey Open-File Report|volume=87-297|access-date=2010-08-15|archive-date=2010-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100608213840/http://vulcan.wr.usgs.gov/Hazards/NRC_Report/nrc_hazards.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。火山泥和[[混凝土|混凝土]]相似，流動時是[[液態|液態]]，停止時則是[[固態|固態]]。<ref name="usgswhat">{{cite web|url=http://volcanoes.usgs.gov/Hazards/What/Lahars/lahars.html|title=Lahars and Their Effects|work=USGS Volcano Hazards Program|accessdate=2007-09-02|archive-date=2007-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070824150316/http://volcanoes.usgs.gov/Hazards/What/Lahars/lahars.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[美國|美國]]的[[瑞尼爾山|瑞尼爾山]]、印尼的[[加隆貢火山|加隆貢火山]]和[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]]的[[魯阿佩胡山|魯阿佩胡山]]的火山泥流風險最高，其中瑞尼爾山在5,600年前發生火山泥流，330平方公里的地方受火山泥影響<ref name="Crandall">{{cite journal|last=Crandall|first=D.R.|year=1971|title=Postglacial Lahars From Mount Rainier Volcano, Washington|journal=U.S. Geological Survey Professional Paper|volume=677|url=http://vulcan.wr.usgs.gov/Volcanoes/Rainier/Publications/PP677/osceola_mudflow.html|access-date=2010-08-15|archive-date=2010-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100607150405/http://vulcan.wr.usgs.gov/Volcanoes/Rainier/Publications/PP677/osceola_mudflow.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。近年造成重大傷亡的火山泥流發生在1985年，當時[[哥倫比亞|哥倫比亞]][[內瓦多·德·魯伊斯火山|內瓦多·德·魯伊斯火山]]爆發導致火山泥流，鄰近城市[[阿爾梅羅|阿爾梅羅]]被5米深的山泥淹埋，造成約23,000居民死亡，佔當地人口的四分之三。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://volcanoes.usgs.gov/Hazards/What/Lahars/RuizLahars.html|title=Deadly Lahars from Nevado del Ruiz, Colombia|work=USGS Volcano Hazards Program|accessdate=2007-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070824150301/http://volcanoes.usgs.gov/Hazards/What/Lahars/RuizLahars.html|archive-date=2007-08-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

